## 4. Database Schema

```mermaid
erDiagram
    USERS {
        ObjectId _id
        String name
        String email
        String password
        String role "student | teacher"
        Number points
        Array badges
        Date createdAt
    }

    QUIZZES {
        ObjectId _id
        String title
        String subject
        String topic
        String difficulty "easy | medium | hard"
        Array questions "{ question, options[], correctAnswer }"
        ObjectId createdBy
        Date createdAt
    }

    QUIZ_ATTEMPTS {
        ObjectId _id
        ObjectId userId
        ObjectId quizId
        Array answers
        Number score
        Number timeTaken
        Date completedAt
    }

    STUDENT_PROGRESS {
        ObjectId _id
        ObjectId userId
        String subject
        Object topicScores "{ topicName: avgScore }"
        String currentLevel "beginner | intermediate | advanced"
        Array recommendations
        Date updatedAt
    }

    BADGES {
        ObjectId _id
        String name
        String description
        String icon
        String criteria "e.g. score_100, streak_7"
    }

    USERS ||--o{ QUIZ_ATTEMPTS : takes
    USERS ||--o{ STUDENT_PROGRESS : has
    USERS ||--o{ BADGES : earns
    QUIZZES ||--o{ QUIZ_ATTEMPTS : attempted_in
```

---

## 5. API Design

### Auth APIs
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | Register student/teacher |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Login → returns JWT |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Get current user profile |

### Quiz APIs
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/quizzes` | List quizzes (filter by subject, difficulty) |
| GET | `/api/quizzes/:id` | Get quiz details with questions |
| POST | `/api/quizzes` | Create quiz (teacher only) |
| POST | `/api/quizzes/:id/submit` | Submit quiz answers → get score |

### AI / Recommendation APIs
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/ai/recommendations` | Get personalized recommendations for student |
| GET | `/api/ai/study-tips/:subject` | Get AI-generated study tips |

### Student APIs
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/student/progress` | Get student's progress across subjects |
| GET | `/api/student/analytics` | Get strengths/weaknesses analysis |
| GET | `/api/student/history` | Get quiz attempt history |

### Teacher APIs
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/teacher/students` | List all students |
| GET | `/api/teacher/students/:id/progress` | View specific student's progress |
| POST | `/api/teacher/assign` | Assign quiz to students |

### Gamification APIs
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/gamification/leaderboard` | Get top students by points |
| GET | `/api/gamification/badges` | Get student's badges |

