## 7. 8-Hour Build Timeline

| Hour | Task | Deliverable |
|------|------|-------------|
| **0-1** | Setup + Auth | Project scaffold, MongoDB, JWT auth, login/register |
| **1-2** | Quiz Engine | Quiz model, CRUD APIs, quiz player UI |
| **2-3** | AI Engine | Rule-based scoring, Gemini integration, recommendations API |
| **3-4** | Student Dashboard | Progress charts, analytics, recommendations display |
| **4-5** | Teacher Dashboard | Student list, progress viewer, quiz assignment |
| **5-6** | Gamification | Points system, badges, leaderboard |
| **6-7** | UI Polish | Animations, responsive design, dark mode |
| **7-8** | Deploy + Demo | Vercel + Render deploy, seed data, demo prep |

---

## 8. Key Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Gemini API rate limits | AI features break | Cache responses; fallback to static tips |
| Time overrun on AI engine | No core feature | Build rules first (30 min), add LLM later |
| MongoDB Atlas connectivity | App unusable | Use local MongoDB as fallback |
| Auth bugs | Can't login | Test auth first before building features |

